ny - any payment for it, you see, no, no, if - if you supplied them with the - with the - soles - they would put them on and - leave their own work to do it. Yes, oh yes, all - the repairing of shoes was - I just had to take them to a certain man and he -
 if he was - going off to another job he would put it aside and - do them. Och - these things have all gone you know. And it - and - oh yes. Yes, they were - we're deteriorating in that respect. Oh - oh well -
