l broken, and - he says, he went down to mend it and - and - and I went down with him. And - he said - that day they were learning the alphabet. So he says, I learnt the alphabet. He says, can you say the alphabet? He says, I - I think so. He said, let me
 
hear it. So he had to go through the alphabet. He says, that's very good, he says, that - that's right. He said, now, he says, can you say it backwards? Well - he says, I - I'm sorry - we didn't learn it that way. But, he says, I can say it backwards, he 
