,
 and it was made by - Allison Simm's father. Alistair - Simm - Simm's - Simm's father was in Edinburgh, he was a tailor in Edinburgh. It was made in Edinburgh. I knew his mother very well and of course I used to sing in the same choir as her in Edinburgh.

