ay as good as ever. You know, when I had it for - for twelve or thirteen years I thought I'd better - save it up, and I got another one. The one's - much - poorer looking than it is nowadays. Yes. Callum Johnston. But my mother's name - my grandmother's -
 fair - fair means bad. Yes. My - grandmother's name was McDonald.
